a = hj.Jet(7, [1, 2])
b = a.enlarge(right=1)
assert_equal(len(b), 3)
assert_equal(b.f, 7)
assert_array_almost_equal(b.g, [1, 2, 0])
b = a.enlarge(left=1)
assert_equal(len(b), 3)
assert_equal(b.f, 7)
assert_array_almost_equal(b.g, [0, 1, 2])
b = a.enlarge(right=1, left=1)
assert_equal(len(b), 4)
assert_equal(b.f, 7)
assert_array_almost_equal(b.g, [0, 1, 2, 0])
